(27, 'SEO', 'bImage6315b5ba7184f0.png', 'Can too much SEO lower your ranking?', 'can-too-much-seo-lower-your-ranking', '<p>Too Much SEO</p><p>Yes, it can, just as it did when we partied too much right before our midterms. If you over-optimize your website for the sake of improving its visibility, chances are Google may see your content as <strong>‘trying too hard\'</strong> might not rank it at all.</p><p>Google May Become Wary Of Your Website</p><p>Overusing keywords, linking to irrelevant websites, or choosing irrelevant keywords merely to increase page visits are the simplest ways to escape Google\'s detection. Google will soon begin to view your website as \"fishy,\" and will attentively examine its content.</p><blockquote><p><i>Focus on the searcher\'s intention This should serve as the basis for all of your endeavours, including development and dissemination. What exactly is the searcher seeking to accomplish, and how does your material help them get there?</i></p></blockquote><p>You can be labeled as an SEO spammer</p><p>Google may impose restrictions on the visibility of your content once it verifies the spamming techniques being used on your website. Due to its \"No compromise\" approach, it seeks to ensure that only the most pertinent and accurate information is presented to its users. Additionally, even if your content is appropriate, your promotion strategies might not be.</p><p>Your advertisement may move back to page two or perhaps further.</p><p>Google may gradually stop displaying your ad for searches related to your business and start favoring other websites that are similar to yours, which could result in a decline in ad position.</p><p>Your advertisement may move back to page two or perhaps further.</p><p>But it\'s possible. Utilizing excessive SEO could result in the removal of your website from SERP. Your advertising can also rank so low that no one will ever see them.</p><p>How Much SEO Is Too Much?</p><p>While increasing website traffic is the goal, relying solely on the SEO strategies that have been advocated online is not the best course of action. It\'s crucial to know which techniques will work best for you. The following list of frequent SEO blunders could harm your website\'s traffic.</p><p>Excessive Stuffing of keywords</p><p>Let\'s be clear about one thing: it\'s acceptable to begin with simple terms. The clever Google algorithm will display your adverts for keywords that are similar to the ones you have selected. Therefore, there is no need to pack your goods in every potential variation (cake and cakes are the same). So, concentrate on 7–10 keywords that are highly trafficked, have medium–low competition, and are directly relevant to your business. Utilize keyword planning tools like Google\'s Keyword Planner, Moz, Semrush, etc. to determine which keywords would be effective for you.</p><p>All Internal and External Links That Lead To The Website\'s Home Page.</p><p>Although it\'s excellent to add connections to your website\'s home page, you must remember that users are more interested in your content than you are. Therefore, when visitors click on a link that promises vegan pasta recipes, they prefer to see those recipes right away rather than being taken to the homepage of a blog on veganism and then having to search for the recipes there. The better, the more approachable your content should be.</p><p>Linking Too Much To Spam Websites</p><p>The content of the websites you\'ve linked to is just as crucial to SEO as your own content. Your credibility may suffer if you point users toward spammy or pointless websites. Additionally, refrain from keyword stuffing and excessive linking. Only look at a few (ideally one or two) links to appropriate websites.</p><p>Choosing SEO Over Good Content</p><p>When attempting to attract a sizable audience through your website, it\'s simple to become lost in the complexities of SEO. However, if your content isn\'t what people are seeking for, no amount of SEO will ever be able to help you.Therefore, focus on what your customers want from you and deliver on it. Always focus on your brand before your marketing strategy. What you intend to promote must, after all, be promotable.</p>', 'Akangsha Gautam', 'Can too much SEO lower your ranking?', 'META DESCRIPTION *Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit,', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'META KEYWORDS * Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit,', 'IT,SEO,SMO,DATA', 1, '2022-09-05 08:39:22', 0, '2022-09-28 07:54:39', 0),
(37, 'Mobile App Development', 'bImage631b0346aa6d70.webp', 'Top 10 Technologies used for Rapid App Development', 'top-10-technologies-used-for-rapid-app-development', '<p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>The most widely used&nbsp;<strong>rapid app development</strong> technologies are revolutionizing the lives of those who use them. Among the most well-known are:</i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>1. WebAssembly</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>WebAssembly is another significant achievement in the field of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/services/rapid-app-development\"><strong>rapid app development</strong></a>. This is regarded as JavaScript\'s closest buddy, with some proclaiming the dawn of JavaScript, which is a small and quick parallel configuration that ensures near local execution for web applications. WebAssembly can help designers create fast online applications, which are particularly important in games, music, CAD applications, video editing, and transmission.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>2. Movement User Interface (UI) Design</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Clients today want a remarkable customer experience, and the key to engaging target audiences is a superior user interface that is simple to use and incorporates natural safe data flow. Clients will flock to website pages that have appealing and intuitive components as well as an engaging page format, resulting in higher harp time on site pages. Innovative enlivened headers and pennants, vivified outlines, foundation liveliness, and drift impacts are some of the best technologies for website creation. They give life to pages and draw in clients.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>3. Utilization of Chatbots</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When you\'re using a Chatbot, it will improve your online assistance by providing more options for your customers. According to a NewVoiceMedia research report, businesses in the United States lose over $62 million per year due to poorly organized client administrations. Chatbots are widely trusted to provide excellent customer service. You will also benefit from the assistance provided on a daily basis. As a result, you may save the salary of a full-time online customer service agent and put it towards something more reachable.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>4. Artificial Intelligence</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Artificial intelligence which is a man-made brainpower is expected to reach $3.9 trillion by 2022, according to Gartner. Many organizations are incorporating AI into their advanced transformation strategy, and there are no signs that this trend will slow down. Babylon by TELUS Health just released a free social insurance&nbsp;<strong>mobile application development</strong> that allows you to check symptoms, communicate with professionals, and access your health records. The programme, which was developed by a talented team of experts and academics, goes above and beyond standard online health advice by combining artificial intelligence (AI) with true face-to-face meetings.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>5. Dynamic Web Applications (PWA)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Dynamic Web Applications are the next big thing in the world of adaptable Apps and web development solutions. It is a portable application that does not require the installation of a portable software. PWA provides clients with applications such as instant understanding in their programmes because of its excellent web capabilities. This is slanting and gaining strength due to its ability to function independently and match material to numerous technologies.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>6. Blockchain</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Blockchain has altered the effectiveness of development as well as security and information technology. Blockchain is a well-known record breakthrough that makes it possible to keep data across multiple employees. Allowing everyone on the system to view each other\'s entry in a near-constant stream. Making it impossible for customers to manipulate or influence the system.</p><p>Money-related, educational, and human-services departments have all embraced blockchain developments, which are predicted to generate a staggering $10.6 billion in revenue by 2023.<br>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>7. Flourishing message pop-ups</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>A path in mobile app development, or a website with pop-up notifications, could result in a huge number of visitors. This can be used in a web-based advertising system as well.</p><p>Pop-up messages are widely recognised as one of the most effective ways to capture visitors\' and clients\' attention. As a result, find a web developer who is aware of the importance of this topic. In any case, you should avoid abusing them. They allow you to educate clients on appealing limitations, helpful exercises, and other issues.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>8. Single Page Applications (SPA)</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>A single page application (SPA) is a web application or website that interacts with the user by progressively updating the current page rather than stacking new pages from a worker. This method will prevent client communication on sequential pages from being disrupted. SPA eliminates the need for guests to navigate difficult menus by adapting to any device.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>9. Web Server Software</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The word \"web worker\" can refer to either the hardware (a physical computer) or the software (a computer programme) that provides your website to the end user for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/\"><strong>website development</strong></a>. Because we\'re talking about layers of your site\'s innovation cake, we\'re referring to the product of the worker who makes your site work. The web worker is the layer that sits between the Operating System and the rest of the cake. The decision is typically made depending on the several advancements you\'re employing as well as the location of your website. The two web workers that control the Internet are Apache (Linux) and IIS (Windows) (Microsoft).</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>10. Computerized Transformation</strong></h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Computerized change can be intimidating, so each industry must prepare for the next one. Many firms who formerly used traditional CMS are switching to Headless CMS. Headless is a CMS designed specifically for static sites that may be integrated with a variety of stages via various gadgets. It has the potential to be used for an extended period of time and is quickly becoming a regular way of content delivery. When compared to traditional CMS, the headless CMS offers greater benefits to any&nbsp;<strong>website development company</strong>.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', 'Akangsha Gautam', 'Top 10 Technologies used for Rapid App Development', 'Looking for rapid app development company? Codepilot Technologies Private Limited helps you to digitize your business process. Call: +917635960463', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'rapid app development, app development platform, app development model, app development open source, app development software, app development tools, app development company near me, what\'s rapid app development, web development, software, software development, software development company, software development company in guwahati, digital transformation, data analytics, custom product development, app development company in guwahati, android app development, iOS app development, mobile app development, assam, guwahati, barcelona, berlin, amsterdam, warsaw, new york, san francisco, chicago, los angeles, washington, miami, nashville, texas, dubai, kuwait city, muscat, abu dhab', 'rapid app development, app development platform, app development model, app development open source, app development software, app development tools, software development, software development company, android app development, iOS app development, mobile app development, guwahati, barcelona, berlin, amsterdam, warsaw, new york, san francisco, chicago, los angeles, washington, texas', 1, '2022-09-09 09:11:34', 0, '2022-10-06 07:07:28', 0),
(38, 'Business and Companies', 'bImage63244973e263d0.webp', 'What Makes a Business Technically Necessary', 'what-makes-a-business-technically-necessary', '<h3><strong>Using Codepilot Technologies Arena to Increase the Value of a Business Glossary</strong></h3><p>People that frequently handle raw data, like Data Stewards, are far more likely to make an error that could lead to unreliable results. Business glossaries are extremely helpful to stewards because they enable them to confirm the definitions of terms or entities and, as a result, eliminate the possibility of giving data consumers false information.</p><p>The <a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/\"><strong>Codepilot Technologies</strong></a> Arena DataOps platform makes it easier than ever to create and maintain them across a company\'s complete data environment. Data engineers can create automated workflows to apply to a certain entity or data collection using the defined business glossary terms in the platform. The phrases are also used by data analysts and data scientists to access and search the platform\'s data catalog. These are just a few instances of how an Arena business lexicon is assisting organizations in making the most of their data and effectively achieving their corporate objectives.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Why is a business glossary useful and what does it mean?</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;An organization\'s list of terms and meanings used in regular business operations is called a business glossary. Companies may ensure that everyone using a glossary of terms to analyze company data understands and uses the same definitions. A standard set of business concepts must be understood by all members of the organization in order to provide accurate internal or external reporting and confident, data-driven decision making. They enable businesses to offer the required proof of regulatory compliance for a data governance programme, which makes them an essential component of developing proper data governance architecture and processes.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Constructing a Glossary Structure</strong></h3><p>&nbsp;A corporation can start formalizing a glossary to concisely list and clarify business concepts after it is able to compile all of the terminology in one location. Each phrase on the list can either identify a concept or an entity that is clearly identifiable by a name that is distinctive to the organization and defined by that description. As this glossary aims to standardize interpretation of frequently used business ideas and their proper settings, definitions should be defined in a language that everyone in the organization can understand.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Using the Business Glossary</strong></h3><p>A business glossary that uses the appropriate terminology in the right context reduces the possibility of sharing inaccurate information on reports and helps employees avoid reporting errors in calculations or potential data analytics inaccuracies. It adds that additional layer of comprehension to help workers avoid costly errors.</p><p>The Dataedo blog post \"What is the Business Value of a Business Glossary?\" offers a straightforward yet potent illustration of a problem that may develop in the absence of a business glossary. Although it may seem unimportant, certain businesses use the phrases \"client\" and \"customer\" differently. This is because they have distinct meanings in different settings. Both phrases refer to \"a person making a purchase,\" however for some companies, a \"client\" is someone who requests professional services from a business, whereas a \"customer\" purchases items or services from a business. Additional examples include the business glossaries of financial institutions, which may include the phrases Fiduciary and Prime Rate, and healthcare organizations, which may include the terms Glucose and Point of Care (POC). Due to the internal definitions of common business procedures, every company lexicon is distinct and never exactly matches another.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>Recap of the Glossary</strong></h3><p>Clarity is key to unlocking a range of organizational-wide benefits, and creating and implementing a business lexicon that is an easily accessible tool and a crucial part of the organization\'s policies and processes supports that clarity. They are essential for encouraging cross-team cooperation, preserving data quality, enhancing data transparency, and guaranteeing that everyone is conversant in business jargon. Scroll the website, join up for a guided free trial, or organize a demo with Codepilot\'s data professionals to find out more about how the Arena DataOps platform from Codepilot Technologies might change your company\'s business glossary.</p><p><br><br>&nbsp;</p>', 'Akangsha Gautam', 'What Makes a Business Technically Necessary', 'A list of business words and their definitions is used by companies to guarantee that the same phrases are used throughout the company while evaluating data', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 'bussiness, business glossary, data, data analytics, assam, guwahati', 'business,business glossary,dataOps platform,assam, guwahati, barcelona, berlin, amsterdam, warsaw, new york, san francisco, chicago, los angeles, washington, miami, nashville, texas, dubai, kuwait city,muscat, abu dhab,digital transformation, data analytics, custom product development', 1, '2022-09-16 10:01:23', 0, '2022-09-16 11:00:46', 0),
(39, 'Software Development Company', 'akib__1663928890.webp', 'Software Development Company in Guwahati, India', 'software-development-company-in-guwahati-india', '<p>The top software companies not only rule domestically but are also among the top outsourcing and IT providers in the world. The Indian software sector has historically been a key component of the economy of the nation. The software has grown to play a significant role in today\'s society. We constantly rely on software in both our personal and professional lives. Most importantly, many businesses rely on software to complete their tasks and keep their operations run smoothly. As a result, many structured businesses provide software development services. There are several software companies in Guwahati that provide a wide range of programs with different features.&nbsp;</p><p>Hire a top provider to handle your software needs if you want to expand your business internationally. By creating robust, safe, and high-performing software solutions,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/\"><strong>Codepilot</strong> <strong>Technologies</strong>&nbsp; </a>provides organizations with top-notch quality services with an excellent user experience.</p><h3><strong>What are the benefits of working with a software company?</strong></h3><p>Companies that develop software deal almost every day with enterprise resource planning systems. To make operations faster, they plan and implement modules that can be automated. Working with a software company provides businesses with custom software that addresses a specific need such as automation, increased productivity, data security, or greater customer engagement. It can also combine several features to create a multi-functional platform used by all organizational aspects.</p><h3><strong>How can software reduce expenses in business?</strong></h3><p>More and more businesses are deciding to digitize their operations in the post-pandemic world to increase operational effectiveness and guarantee business continuity. The pandemic increased the need to cut software development costs, and many executives now prioritize IT cost optimization and reduction as a key priority.</p><p>However, some businesses think that managing software is challenging and that they need to be technically sound, but that is inaccurate. In this digital age where everything is digital, your rivals are gaining new technology to boost the efficiency of their operations and general administration.</p><p>You can access a wide range of information derived from data reports using automated tools. These data reports will help you find possibilities to reduce specific business expenses and negotiate for a better deal to boost ROI.</p><h3><strong>Our various types of software include:</strong></h3><p>As one of the leading software development companies in India, we provide a range of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/services/custom-software-development\"><strong>custom software development</strong>&nbsp;</a>services from India to different locations.</p><h4><strong>Enterprise resource planning (ERP)</strong></h4><p>The term \"ERP\" normally refers to a class of business management software that is typically a suite of interconnected applications. An organization can use ERP to gather, store, organize, and comprehend data from various business processes.<strong>&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;In recent years, ERP solutions have evolved into web-based applications that users can access remotely. The benefits of ERP include free flow of information between business areas, accurate, real-time data reporting, and a single source of information. This solution has both local and cloud deployment options. ERP provides an integrated and constantly updated picture of key business activities using shared databases maintained by a database management system. ERP systems monitor the status of company commitments such as orders, purchase orders, and payroll as well as financial resources such as cash, raw materials, manufacturing capacity, and labor.</p><h4><strong>Billing Software Management System</strong></h4><p>Managing your billing is easy with billing management software. This application allows users to create and send estimates, invoices, acknowledgements, and reminders. Our billing software is excellent for both accountants and non-accountants since it is simple to implement and operate. This software makes use of a professional layout that includes all the crucial information, such as optimal billing practices.&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Inventory Management System&nbsp;</strong></h4><p>Most people are aware that moving inventory makes money; but, without a comprehensive understanding of your items from the time of receipt to the time of shipment, your biggest asset may be costing you money. The key to an efficient and profitable business is complete visibility into the inventory process from start to finish, as well as management tools that help you maintain optimal stock levels year-round. An efficient inventory management system assists you in streamlining all the moving components of your warehouse, from suggesting the ideal stock levels to maintaining an organized and efficient supply chain.</p><p>Make your business stand out by partnering with us. With the help of the services offered by Codepilot Technologies, you can restructure your business and adapt to changes in modern technology.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/contact\"><strong>Contact us</strong>&nbsp;</a>for a free consultation and demo if you\'re looking for a software company in Guwahati. Our software engineers created high-quality software that satisfies industry standards and has a sizable clientele in Guwahati, Assam.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Bipasha Goswami', 'Software Development Company in Guwahati, India', 'Confused with the kind of software your business needs? Codepilot Technologies is the leading software company in Guwahati, India. Call +917635960463 now', 'https://www.codepilot.in/blog/software-development-company-in-guwahati-india', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'software development, app development software, software development tools, software development company near me, software development company, software development company in guwahati, software development company in india, custom software development, custom software development company in guwahati, digital transformation, data analytics, custom product development, app development company in guwahati, android app development, iOS app development, mobile app development, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, berlin, boston, amsterdam, warsaw, new york, san francisco, chicago, los angeles, washington, miami, seattle, nashville, texas, houston, dubai, kuwait city, jaipur, bengaluru, mumbai,muscat, abu dhab, delhi, hyderabad', 'software development company near me, software development company, software development company in guwahati, software development company in india, custom software development company in guwahati, custom product development, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, berlin, boston, amsterdam, warsaw, new york, san francisco, chicago, los angeles, washington, miami, seattle, nashville, texas, houston, dubai, kuwait city, jaipur, bengaluru, mumbai,muscat, abu dhab, delhi, hyderabad', 1, '2022-09-23 10:03:01', 0, '2022-10-28 09:17:55', 0),
(41, 'Trending', 'bImage6333ff2bd8ce00.webp', 'Now experience MetaPujo in 2022', 'now-experience-metapujo-in-2022', '<p>This year Durga Puja has entered the world of Metaverse. Yes, you heard that right. Now you can enjoy pandal hopping from anywhere around the world. This year&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.metaform.com/#home\"><strong>Metaform</strong></a> and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.xpand-land.com/\"><strong>XP&amp;DLand</strong>&nbsp;</a>along with Puja committees of&nbsp;Ahiritola Sarbojanin, Deshapriya Park, Ballygunge Cultural and Tala Prattay have arranged a metaverse platform for Durga Puja and named it MetaPujo which&nbsp; will be accessible through 3D twins on the Metaverse.<br>&nbsp;</p><p>“The worlds of digital and real life are colliding, where we will constantly toggle between the real and metaverse worlds in the future. This is the first time in history that such a massive festival of devotion has been twinned in the Metaverse. We are piloting it with four pandals this year, with over 100 next year, and in the near future, every single pandal on the ground will have a metaverse twin for people to experience and enjoy,” said Sukrit Singh, co-founder of Metaform &amp; XP&amp;DLand.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>MetaPujo NFT Collection</h3><p>As a memento of their darshan on Metaverse, devotees can gather NFTs of the god from the different pandals. This year’s Durga Puja is unique and the combination of real life and virtual reality is experimental and fun too.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With the use of 3D recreations of the pandals, users of the metaverse platform \"Spatial\" will be able to enter a shared social space where individuals from all over the world may congregate and walk around, interact, and even snap pictures. In a matter of minutes, users can create a meta-realistic avatar of themselves. All users can access the platform via basic smart phones, tablets, and wearables.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Suppose you stay in Guwahati and your friends stay in Bangalore and Canada, you all can enjoy the MetapPujo together. Metaverse is making the impossible into reality and having your close ones near during festive season through Metaverse is just a gift from technology.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p><p>“This initiative gives Maa Durga an enhanced address on Web 3.0 where the devotees from across the world will be able to enter a three-dimensional recreation of the pandals and take part in darshans from the most popular pandals of Kolkata,”Sukrit&nbsp; Singh notes.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Rimpa Mondal', 'Now experience MetaPujo in 2022', 'Metaform and XP&DLand along with Puja committees in kolkata have arranged a metaverse platform for Durga Puja. Take a look at what\'s new here.', 'https://www.codepilot.in/blog/now-experience-metapujo-in-2022', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'metapujo, metaverse, augmented reality, virtual reality, durga puja, durga puja 2022, metaverse durga puja, deshpriya park, tala park, bengal, guwahati, assam, india, calgary, alberta, canada, dublin, ireland, nashville, India, chille, south africa, USA', 'metapujo,metaverse,augmented reality,virtual reality,durga puja,kolkata,metaform,nfts,guwahati,assam,india,calgary,alberta,canada,dublin,ireland', 1, '2022-09-28 08:00:43', 0, '2022-10-28 09:18:52', 0),
(43, 'Mobile App Development', 'akib__1664535740.webp', 'Mobile App Development: 5 Reasons Your Business Needs It', 'mobile-app-development-5-reasons-your-business-needs-it', '<p>The world today is surrounded by technology, and practically everyone, regardless of age, now uses mobile devices. Smartphone use has become a requirement due to the popularity of its smart functions and features. In today\'s technologically advanced and fiercely competitive business environment, every company must draw in clients and for that, they must work to attract customers. This includes relying on devices like smartphones and tablets. Regardless of the industry, every business should provide its customers with a mobile solution to sell them goods or spread awareness of the services they provide.</p><p>Most mobile device users, on average, look up products or services online and browse via mobile apps related to those products. At this point, you might be thinking that your small business doesn\'t need a mobile app to sell products to your loyal customers. That\'s not the case, though. That might have been true in the past, but if you want to position your business for the future, you must create a mobile app with the best&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/services/app-development\"><strong>mobile app development</strong>&nbsp;<strong>company</strong></a>.</p><p>Businesses from all around the world now have begun to switch to mobile apps! Let\'s go over the five benefits of getting&nbsp;<strong>mobile application development</strong> services to create the best mobile app for your business in case you\'re still not convinced.&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>1. Increased Visibility</strong></h3><p>Having a mobile app helps businesses reach their clients more easily. It is almost impossible to reach each customer manually and tell them about the services you offer.</p><p>There are a great deal of people who use smartphones nowadays. As a result, customers are more accessible to the business. Therefore businesses rely more on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/\"><strong>mobile app developers&nbsp;</strong></a>nowadays to develop mobile applications.</p><h3 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>2. Cultivate Customer Loyalty</strong></h3><p>Effective consumer engagement ensures a high rate of customer retention. Mobile applications that offer customer-focused services or goods will attract more user attention. As a result, a business will continue to communicate with its customers, which encourages growth. Thus, a mobile app encourages customer loyalty and makes it simpler for them to get in touch with you whenever they want.</p><p>Within your app, you can build a brand loyalty program that facilitates better deals. For instance, advertising and promotions displayed through mobile applications are more effective than banner ads and ads on social media.</p><h3><strong>3. Better Brand Recognition</strong></h3><p>It is quite evident that a brand could be recognized for a variety of things. However, several notable aspects stand out, such as social media presence, graphics, and excellent customer service. But, despite that, USP continues to be the most important element of a brand. The business\'s credibility and reputation are formed by how well it solves a problem.</p><p>Now you might be thinking about how mobile apps aid in establishing brand recognition. Well, mobile applications enable fast raise brand recognition. The fact that a user downloaded your app means that they are expecting something impressive from it. So instead of just providing them with information on your website, provide them with additional valuable services.</p><p>On the other hand, every business strives to rule its sector. Having a mobile app for your business can help you get more visibility in the market, and if you offer a mobile app solution to your loyal customers, you can dominate the market for a very long time. Consequently, a mobile app increases brand awareness, which aids in boosting profitability.</p><h3><strong>4. Direct Marketing</strong></h3><p>For a corporation to bring significant rewards, effective marketing is necessary. Because of the steady advancement of technology, we no longer follow any prior marketing trends. You no longer need a salesperson to engage with customers and promote your business. It can be advertised with the use of an intuitive mobile application.&nbsp;</p><p>By continuously delivering notifications of sales and promotional offers to users\' smartphones, it helps to draw in more business. Users can use a mobile app to get more information about the deals.&nbsp;</p><p>One of the most important periods to attract customers is during the sale period. A mobile app includes everything, including information, booking forms, accounts, newsfeeds, and more. By using push notifications, you can remind your customers about your services and make them aware of your offers.</p><h3><strong>5. Rise in Profits</strong></h3><p>Profits are every company\'s ultimate objective. There are differences between the percentage of sales made with and without a mobile app. One technique to boost a company\'s earnings is through a mobile app.</p><p>Also&nbsp;the level of customer satisfaction directly correlates with the level of sales. It is essential to have a responsive website that can adjust to any screen, regardless of size. However, you\'ll notice a remarkable increase in your sales and profit if you also release a mobile app for your company.</p><p>Both a mobile applications and a website have benefits for businesses. A website provides all the necessary details about the company. A mobile app, however, converts users into leads.</p><h3><strong>Conclusion</strong></h3><p>Looking for a technology-driven mobile app to advance in the market?&nbsp;This blog will be helpful to companies looking to invest in the creation of&nbsp;<strong>mobile applications</strong>.</p><p><a href=\"https://codepilot.in/contact\"><strong>Contact us</strong></a> to speak with one of our specialists right away. We help your business succeed by turning all of your app concepts into reality.</p>', 'Bipasha Goswami', 'Mobile App Development: 5 Reasons Your Business Needs It', 'Mobile apps are versatile yet they increase the visibility and traffic for a business. Looking for mobile app development company in Guwahati, India? Call: +917635960463', 'https://codepilot.in/blog/mobile-app-development-5-reasons-your-business-needs-it', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'mobileappdevelopment, mobileapp, mobileapplicationdevelopment, appdevelopment, mobileappdeveloper, progressivewebapp, appdevelopmentcompany, appdevelopmentservices, ios, android, guwahati, assam, india, usa, berlin, warsaw, canada, bangalore, nashville, washington, miami', 'Mobile app development,app development,app development company,app development company in guwahati,app development company near me,IOS app ,android app,Guwahati,assam,india,warsaw,delhi,kolkata,berlin,bangalore,nairobi,washington,nashville,miami', 1, '2022-09-30 10:22:05', 0, '2022-10-28 09:19:47', 0),
(44, 'E-commerce', 'bImage633ff5f31dc620.jpg', '7 Tips Towards Successful eCommerce Website Development', '7-tips-towards-successful-ecommerce-website-development', '<p>Ecommerce has gained more popularity than ever before. An e-commerce website gives potential customers the ease of selecting the goods they want to buy, adding them to an online shopping cart, and then paying for them. However, developing a website from scratch takes time and effort. There is a lot of work to be done, from choosing a URL to classifying the products and having a website plan in place.</p><p>Unlike other websites, an eCommerce website is unique. A variety of other factors should be considered, such as SSL configuration, payment choices, site architecture, design, and page load speed.</p><p>One of the unique selling points is the development of an attractive and enticing eCommerce website. The use of colors, patterns, fonts, etc. with consideration for the elements of digital marketing, however, aids in developing brand identification. Having a visually pleasing e-commerce site is evidence of the rise in SEO as it creates interest in the products and services offered.</p><p>Anyhow, a successful e-commerce website is an online store that needs to be updated frequently. Having a great branding strategy on the website is therefore important since it fosters credibility and trust in the brand name. It also attracts customers by relating to your business concept and by addressing their problems and pain points. Access your website as well and consider how quickly it loads, how easy it is to navigate, how long it takes to complete the checkout process, etc.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>These are the top 7 things that must be considered during the process of&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/services/web-application-development\"><strong>eCommerce website development.</strong></a><br>&nbsp;</h3><h4><strong>1.Desired Content</strong></h4><p>Your website\'s content is its essential element. By addressing many of the questions that potential clients may have, the FAQ section of the website also adds value. Likewise, visitors to your e-commerce site develop trust with it. Additionally, since it will be scanned, the material on your website ought to be simple to understand. Short paragraphs and a strong call to action must be included in the content of the websites together with the appropriate subheadings and bullet points. So, to attract online buyers, create an&nbsp;<strong>eCommerce website design</strong> with the content that is specifically relevant to them.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>2. Making the Website Aesthetically Pleasing</strong></h4><p>Most of the credibility of a website comes from its design. An unattractive website may give the impression that it is a fraud or can steal personal information. The long-term growth of an online retailer may suffer if customers lack confidence in the website\'s ability to provide excellent customer service.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li><strong>Including excellent and high-quality photographs on the website</strong></li></ol><p>A website needs to contain high-quality photographs or else the visitor will have a bad impression of it. The chosen photos ought to be appropriate for a website. For instance, a retailer selling the most recent model of a mobile phone online shouldn\'t use an image from a previous generation in a brand-new banner ad.</p><p><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2. Choosing the right theme or template to start with</strong></p><p>Do you want to market to customers who come from different nations and use different currencies? The foundation for an omnichannel and multichannel empire must be strong. The crucial decision after selecting a platform is your theme. You must have a single visually appealing website that is tailored to reflect your brand. This is when your customers interact with your website. It must perform properly and look good.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>3. Make it Mobile Responsive</strong></h4><p>How often have you tried using your phone to browse a website only to discover that a laptop or desktop is required? A website that is challenging to access on a mobile device may have a negative effect on the user experience. Because the majority of people in today\'s society use mobile devices, it is essential to make sure that visitors do not need to repeatedly zoom in to read the content on the page. Therefore, a mobile-optimized website that functions similarly to the web on mobile devices is a requirement for an e-commerce site. By using user-friendly mobile websites, you can attract more customers to your business. To guarantee that all of the website\'s pages are responsive on mobile devices, speak with a reliable&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/\"><strong>eCommerce website development company.</strong></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>4. Contact us/location page has to be created.</strong></h4><p>Simply launching a new e-commerce website is insufficient. If clients\' inquiries aren\'t answered, you run the danger of losing their business without a contact-us option. For a variety of reasons, customers might desire to speak with customer service representatives. For instance, if the website experiences a technical problem, or a client may wish to monitor the box they ordered or let the delivery person know they won\'t be home to receive their order. Any eCommerce website must provide a phone number or email address. It is also important to note that not responding to emails or phone calls from customers can discourage them from making purchases online.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>5. Speed Optimization for both Mobile and Desktop</strong></h4><p>The majority of mobile users leave websites that take longer than three seconds to load. In a market where your competitors are working hard to maintain their e-commerce websites, it might be a huge mistake to overlook the website load time. Any&nbsp;<strong>eCommerce portal&nbsp;</strong>that wants to grow successfully needs to make sure that its load time is quick enough. It is important to consider loading time when it comes to boosting sales since slow loading time leads online buyers to switch over to another site. However, if your e-commerce website has the advantage of a quick loading time, it will probably have more online visibility, which will lead to an increase in sales. Therefore, make sure you build an e-commerce website that loads quickly.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>6. Get recognised with Digital Marketing</strong></h4><p>It is impossible to communicate with your customers in the long run successfully if you don\'t leverage the power of social media. The contact us page of your website can include links to social media platforms where the target customers can receive updates regarding new products and categories on a regular basis.</p><p>Establish a social media profile or link on your e-commerce website and post any new uploads on the user\'s profile. Because a social media presence helps keep a brand current and because it is the ideal medium for drawing the target audience\'s attention. Check out&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/\"><strong>Codepilot Technologies’</strong></a> services to learn more about&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/services/digital-marketing\"><strong>digital marketing</strong></a> optimization and to locate the right social media marketing strategies.<br>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>7. SEO-optimised eCommerce Website&nbsp;</strong></h4><p>By using the top&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/SEO\"><strong>SEO</strong></a> techniques, you may boost the amount of traffic to your website. Here are some tactics you might use based on the importance of the material you have chosen for<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/blog/can-too-much-seo-lower-your-ranking\"><strong> SEO.</strong></a></p><ul><li>Conduct keyword research and strive to include the best keyword in your text</li><li>Using the language that the general audience uses</li><li>Use important words in H1, H2, and other headings.</li></ul><p>Check out our services page if you want help building a user-friendly, eye-catching e-commerce website that helps you stand out from the competition.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/contact\"><strong>Contact us</strong></a> to build an e-commerce platform that fits your needs.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', 'Bipasha Goswami', '7 Tips Towards Successful eCommerce Website Development', 'Here are 7 reasons why businesses should opt for ecommerce website to scale up in long term. Reach us now for free consultation. Call +917635960463', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'website development company,  web development, website design company,  web design company near me, website designing services, eCommerce website development, eCommerce website design, eCommerce website development company, eCommerce website development company near me, eCommerce website development company in guwahati, eCommerce portal, berlin, usa, warsaw, canada, bangalore, mumbai, dubai, nashville, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, boston, amsterdam, chicago, newyork, hyderabad', 'website development company  web development, website design company,  web design company near me, website designing services, eCommerce website development, eCommerce website design, eCommerce website development company, eCommerce website development company in guwahati, eCommerce portal, berlin, usa, warsaw, canada, bangalore, mumbai, dubai, nashville, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, boston, amsterdam, chicago, newyork, hyderabad', 1, '2022-10-07 09:48:35', 0, '2022-10-07 09:57:23', 0);
