(48, 'Website design services', 'bImage6352516e2b3640.png', 'Why is Website Designing Services booming in 2022?', 'why-is-website-designing-services-booming-in-2022', '<p>A uniquely designed website determines the success of a service or company.&nbsp;Regardless of whether they are aware of it or not,&nbsp;people are naturally attracted to aesthetically pleasing designs.</p><p>Website design is becoming increasingly important for companies today. Today, it is essential to have a website so that you can reach out to potential customers online! Despite this, many companies do not understand WHY a high-quality website design is crucial. Let us explain now!</p><p>Having a website design is not enough to create a successful online presence for small businesses. If you didn\'t know it already, your website design has the power to either make or break a deal. The website for your company has great potential to convert visitors into loyal customers. The better the site, the more trust your visitors will have in your business.</p><p>You might be wondering why website design is crucial if you\'ve ever looked for a new business website or redesign your current website. There are a few reasons why you should consider hiring a reputable&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/services/web-application-development\"><strong>website development company</strong></a> and why you should have a decent, attractive website design.</p><h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>1. Makes Navigation Simple</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">A good online platform should be easy for users to navigate for any website that wishes to be ranked higher. Your website\'s users will like how simple it is to navigate. If pages are hard to find, it might affect their experience. In general, the website\'s material should be easy to access, therefore it makes sense to expect the pages to load quickly.</p><h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>2. Helps in Boosting SEO</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Today, the majority of visitors just glance at the first page of websites, and 80% of them only look at the top three search results. If you don\'t show up on the first page of the search engine, your target market will never learn about you or your business. By producing high-quality, a well-designed website will always assist in improving search engines.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Connecting with a reputable web development company that can manage this is one of the best possibilities. Google and other search engines give maximum consideration to websites that follow&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/blog/a-beginners-guide-to-seo\"><strong>SEO guidelines.</strong></a></p><h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>3. Help Your Website to Build Trust&nbsp;</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">It is advantageous to have a visually appealing website because it gives customers an indication of how satisfied they will be with the product or service. The portals that have visual elements and add-on features created by web developers are more likely to get customers easily.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Users hardly ever trust websites that have terrible design. It conveys the wrong impression. If visitors share their reservations about your website looking unprofessional, they may not trust it. &nbsp;Anyone who wants to invest in a product from that website will want to be sure they are investing their money on the right platform and a reliable company.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Let\'s assume the business is reliable, yet the website doesn’t look that appealing. Do you believe the client will want to work with the company? A website that has been expertly made will be more reliable. Because of this, your website should enhance rather than detract from your brand\'s reputation.</p><h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>4. Boost the Sales</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Web design has the power to help you increase sales and improve your company’s revenue. Not only does your site’s design make the first impression, but it has the power to determine if someone becomes a sale for your business.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Users evaluate your site\'s credibility depending on its design when they visit it. Therefore, if your site\'s design is out of date, users will not regard you as trustworthy and will avoid visiting your site.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Consequently, you lose out on sales for your company as a result. Your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/blog/7-tips-towards-successful-ecommerce-website-development\"><strong>website\'s</strong></a> trustworthiness is increased when you redesign its appearance. Visitors will feel at ease browsing or shopping on your page if it has a minimal, clean design.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">They\'re therefore more inclined to make a purchase from your company as a result. However, a well-designed website that provides a favorable user experience will keep visitors on your site longer.</p><h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>5. Attract Lifetime Clients to Your Business</strong></h2><p>Your website has a direct impact on your customer service. If the company wants to develop and expand its wings, it needs loyal customers. However, it could be a challenging endeavor, especially if the entrepreneur uses a mediocre method to do it. The website\'s development and layout are useful at this moment.</p><p>The layout of your websites has a big impact on how well your brand and online presence perform. To fully profit from digital marketing, you must invest in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/\"><strong>website design services</strong></a> that will increase website traffic to learn more about your business.</p><p>We are a full-service web development and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/services/digital-marketing\"><strong>digital marketing</strong></a> agency that focuses on creating unique and stunning websites. Our team of professionals will apply their skills and knowledge to the creation of your website. We can assist you in building a website that your users will enjoy since we understand how important web design is to a niche audience.</p><p>Want to expand your company? Want to increase sales? You have come to the correct place since&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/contact\"><strong>Codepilot Technologies</strong></a> offer top notch web development services to help your business develop and grow.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', 'Bipasha Goswami', 'Why is Website Designing Services booming in 2022?', 'Searching for a website designing company in Guwahati, India? To get your website designed, contact Codepilot Technologies. Call : +91 7635960463', 'https://codepilot.in/blog/why-is-website-designing-services-booming-in-2022', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'website designing service, web application development, software development company, website designing company near me, website designing company, website designing company in guwahati, website designing company in india, custom software development, web development company in guwahati, digital transformation, digital marketing, web application development company in guwahati, android app development, iOS app development, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, berlin, boston, amsterdam, warsaw, new york, san francisco, chicago, los angeles, washington, miami, seattle, nashville, texas, houston, dubai, kuwait city, jaipur, bengaluru, mumbai,muscat, abu dhab, delhi, hyderabad', 'website designing service, web application development, software development company, website designing company near me, website designing company, website designing company in guwahati, website designing company in india, custom software development, web development company in guwahati, digital transformation, digital marketing, web application development company in guwahati, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, berlin, boston, amsterdam, warsaw, new york, san francisco, los angeles, washington, seattle, texas, dubai, bengaluru, mumbai,muscat, delhi,nashville,los angeles,alberta,codepilot technologies,calgary,europe,kolkata', 1, '2022-10-21 07:59:42', 0, '2022-10-21 08:09:10', 0),
(49, 'E-commerce', 'bImage6359066aa3ca50.webp', 'Impact of New E-Commerce Norms on Online Marketing Efforts of E-Commerce Websites', 'impact-of-new-e-commerce-norms-on-online-marketing-efforts-of-e-commerce-websites', '<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">One of the most hotly debated topics has been the future of E-Commerce platforms in India.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/\"><strong>Codepilot Technologies</strong></a> in Guwahati provides the best&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/services/web-application-development\"><strong>e-commerce website design</strong></a>. The recent amendments in the policy regarding E-Commerce in India have created two parallel spheres of public opinion. One sphere advocates in favor of the regulations, saying that it’ll help safeguard the small local shopkeepers who can’t compete with the big players but a contrarian point of view by the other sphere says that such a move is going to severely damage and discourage the E-Commerce space which is still on the rise and contributes heavily to trade. But what exactly happened? How does this impact the density of marketing efforts that these firms put in to compete against each other?&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Impact on E-commerce websites</strong></h2><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">According to the new regulations E-Commerce firms will no longer be able to shower their customers with offers such as hefty discounts, introductory cashback, one-day delivery, or any additional value-added service on their platforms.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In other words, you’ll stop getting cashback notifications from platforms that used to induce customers to shop on their portal instead of lucrative cashback offers.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">This is just one small example of what these regulations imply for the E-Commerce space or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/blog/7-tips-towards-successful-ecommerce-website-development\"><strong>e-commerce portal</strong></a>.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Another major resolution passed by the government prevents any E-Commerce vendor from selling more than one-fourth of its inventory on a particular platform.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">In other words, you won’t see any more Exclusive Launches of smartphones or introductory offers on apparel brands.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">How this will impact the marketing efforts that these firms put in can be gauged from the simple fact the introduction of these reforms is sure to impact a major chunk of their revenue.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Since a cap has been introduced on how much a vendor can sell, the platform loses the advantage of driving in all the revenue from the exclusive sales on its platform.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Secondly, since the products available on these platforms will get more expensive, it will drive customers away who are used to low prices and cashback on their purchases.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">So this move by the government is proving to be a double-edged sword for these E-Commerce platforms and it seems they’ll have to bleed plenty in the coming days. As for you, the customers, be ready to see higher prices and lower offers in the coming days.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', 'Akangsha Gautam', 'Impact of New E-Commerce Norms on Online Marketing Efforts', 'Know about the Impact of New E-Commerce Norms on online marketing efforts of E-Commerce websites. contact now at +917635960463 for free consultation.', 'https://codepilot.in/blog/impact-of-new-e-commerce-norms-on-online-marketing-efforts-of-e-commerce-websites', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'website development company,  web development, website design company,  web design company near me, website designing services, eCommerce website development, eCommerce website design, eCommerce website development company, eCommerce website development company near me, eCommerce website development company in guwahati, eCommerce portal, berlin, usa, warsaw, canada, bangalore, mumbai, dubai, nashville, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, boston, amsterdam, chicago, newyork, hyderabad', 'website development company,  web development, website design company,  web design company near me, website designing services, eCommerce website development, eCommerce website design, eCommerce website development company, eCommerce website development company near me, eCommerce website development company in guwahati, eCommerce portal, berlin, usa, warsaw, canada, bangalore, mumbai, dubai, nashville, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, boston, amsterdam, chicago, newyork, hyderabad', 1, '2022-10-26 10:05:30', 0, '2022-11-18 10:02:59', 0),
(50, 'Mobile App Development', 'bImage635b9be64b2bf0.png', 'Mobile App Development Life Cycle | Design to Deployment', 'mobile-app-development-life-cycle-design-to-deployment', '<p>The number of <a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/services/app-development\"><strong>mobile apps</strong></a> available in app stores has skyrocketed as a result of the growing use of mobile devices. Nearly every aspect of our life now involves apps. The Google Play Store currently has about 3 million apps accessible, according to the most recent estimates.</p><p>Businesses and brands have now started to use apps in order to reach and engage their target audience due to the convenience of using a mobile device. Understanding the mobile app development life cycle therefore can help you know how to get it done perfectly the first time if you too intend to create an application for your audience.&nbsp;</p><p>You\'ll also benefit from knowing what you require and what to anticipate during the development process. The mobile app development and software development life cycle are extremely similar.&nbsp;</p><p>As part of this blog, we will take a deeper look at the four stages and add a few additional elements that work simultaneously to create a process.&nbsp; Generally, there are six steps in the Mobile App Development Life cycle.</p><h2><strong>1: Planning</strong></h2><p>The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/services/app-development\"><strong>Mobile App Development</strong></a> Life Cycle is now in the theoretical stage. The majority of the why and what questions are addressed in the planning phase of the development of a mobile app. It is a stage where you specify the primary justification for using the app and provide more detailed app descriptions.</p><p>Here, you must connect different actions to produce a clear picture of how the process flows. The following five factors should be taken into account at this stage: goals and objectives, mission and vision, target audience, application platform, timing, purpose, price, quality, and methodology.</p><h2><strong>2: Designing and Prototyping</strong></h2><p>This phase of the mobile app development life cycle focuses on the structure and design of the app in particular, as well as creating prototypes that are in line with the goals of the digital product. The actions taken during this step are watched over, assessed, and managed in accordance with the plan for developing a mobile app.</p><h2><strong>3: Coding and Programming</strong></h2><p>The execution or technical stage of the Mobile App Development Life Cycle is where all the action takes place. It is during this step that you will construct your app based on your plan, design, and prototype. To align the activities in this phase with the original plan, advanced monitoring, evaluation, and control measures are required. The experience and skill-set of your programmer or coder is put to the test in this phase of the Mobile App Development Life cycle.</p><h2><strong>4: Testing, Evaluation and Control</strong></h2><p>It is&nbsp; possible that the preceding stage\'s monitoring, assessment, and control approaches are insufficient. In that case, you must test your results against the anticipated deliverables.</p><p>The bugs that surface during use of the software can be fixed by testing it. When you formally distribute the app to your audience, you can personalize the impression you wish to make. You will run quality checks during this step of the mobile app development life cycle.</p><p>The<strong>&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/services/testing-and-qa\"><strong>testing team</strong></a> at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/\"><strong>Codepilot Technologies</strong></a> has always taken a collaborative and transparent approach, believing that this leads to more effective and successful results.&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>5: Introducing Your App</strong></h2><p>The final stage of the development process is often the mobile app\'s release. The level of customer satisfaction is the next to the last in this article because there is another one following it. Your program should now be registered in the appropriate app store, either the Apple App Store or the Google Play Store. It is vital that you use the right platform and focus on your target audience.</p><h2><strong>Step 6: Updating and Maintenance</strong></h2><p>The target audience\'s satisfaction signals the end of the modern mobile app development life cycle. Although finishing the project in step five is an option, it is preferable to complete the process while keeping the client\'s input in mind.</p><p>A user-friendly program must be updated frequently because both technology and customer needs change over time. For the best experience, new releases are essential to improving the first app\'s release.</p><h2><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2><p>Your project\'s success depends on how you coordinate the steps, phases, or stages. With exposure to the app industry, you\'ll be able to incorporate the latest trends, technology, and features into the design of your app.</p><p>There is everything you need to know about creating an app in the modern Mobile App Development Life Cycle. This guide will help you understand what it takes to create a new application from scratch, regardless of how different businesses are. If you\'re interested in learning more about the advantages of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.codepilot.in/blog/mobile-app-development-5-reasons-your-business-needs-it\"><strong>mobile app development</strong></a> for businesses, read our thorough explanation of why your company needs a mobile app to succeed.</p><p>These project execution processes, which include conception (research), design, development, stabilization, deployment, and maintenance, call for expertise, resources, and time.</p><p>Get in touch with<a href=\"https://codepilot.in/contact\"><strong> Codepilot Technologies</strong></a><strong>&nbsp;</strong>to chat with our experts. By making all of your app ideas turn into&nbsp; a reality, we contribute to the success of your business. App creation is not as difficult as it may seem; all it requires are a few careful considerations and advance planning.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', 'Bipasha Goswami', 'Mobile App Development Life Cycle | Design to Deployment', 'Mobile apps are versatile yet they increase the visibility and traffic for a business. Looking for mobile app development company in Guwahati, India? Call: +917635960463', 'https://codepilot.in/blog/mobile-app-development-life-cycle-design-to-deployment', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'mobileappdevelopment, appdevelopmenttools, mobileappdevelopmentcompanynearme, mobileappdevelopmentcompany, mobileappdevelopmentcompanyinguwahati, mobileappdevelopmentcompanyinindia, androidappdevelopment, iOSappdevelopment, mobileapp, appdevelopment, mobileappdeveloper, progressivewebapp, appdevelopmentcompany, appdevelopmentservices, ios, android, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, berlin, boston, amsterdam, warsaw, newyork, sanfrancisco, chicago, losangeles, washington, miami, seattle, nashville, texas, houston, dubai, bengaluru, mumbai, delhi, hyderabad, usa, berlin, canada', 'mobile app development, app development tools, mobile app development company near me, mobile app development company, mobile app development company in guwahati, mobile app development company in india, android app development, iOS app development, mobile app development, assam, guwahati, india, barcelona, berlin, boston, amsterdam, warsaw, new york, san francisco, chicago, los angeles, washington, miami, seattle, nashville, texas, houston, dubai, kuwait city, bengaluru, mumbai,muscat, abu dhab, delhi, hyderabad,canada', 1, '2022-10-28 09:07:50', 0, '2022-10-28 11:08:16', 0);
