(10, 'Mobile App Development', 'mobile-app-development', '<p><strong>Mobile app development</strong> is the act or process by which a mobile app is developed for mobile devices, such as personal digital assistants, enterprise digital assistants or mobile phones. These software applications are designed to run on mobile devices, such as a smartphone or tablet computer. These applications can be pre-installed on phones during manufacturing platforms, or delivered as web applications using server-side or client-side processing (e.g., JavaScript) to provide an \"application-like\" experience within a web browser.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-09-09 09:00:32', 1, NULL, NULL),
(11, 'Business and Companies', 'business-and-companies', '<p>Business and Companies</p>', '2022-09-16 09:38:28', 1, NULL, NULL),
(12, 'Software Development Company', 'software-development-company', '<p>Codepilot Technologies is the leading software company in Guwahati, India. Working with a software company provides businesses with custom software that addresses a specific need such as automation, increased productivity, data security, or greater customer engagement. It can also combine several features to create a multi-functional platform used by all organisational aspects.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-09-23 09:25:34', 1, '2022-09-23 09:26:46', 1),
(13, 'Trending', 'trending', '<p>Treding news on lastest technologies, programming languages and new inventions.</p>', '2022-09-28 07:54:41', 1, NULL, NULL),
(14, 'Mobile App Development', 'mobile-app-development', '<p>Mobile apps are versatile yet they increase the visibility and traffic for a business. Looking for mobile app development company in Guwahati, India? Call: +917635960463</p>', '2022-09-30 10:03:01', 1, NULL, NULL),
(15, 'E-commerce', 'e-commerce', '<p>An e-commerce website gives potential customers the ease of selecting the goods they want to buy, adding them to an online shopping cart, and then paying for them.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-10-07 09:33:25', 1, NULL, NULL),
(16, 'Digital Marketing', 'digital-marketing', '<p>Digital marketing is the component of marketing that uses the Internet and online based digital technologies such as desktop computers, mobile phones and other digital media and platforms to promote products and services.</p>', '2022-10-11 08:55:21', 1, NULL, NULL),
(17, 'Custom Software Development', 'custom-software-development', '<p>With custom software development, a business can precisely define the tasks, features, and other specifications that they want the software to perform for them. Because of its expanded capability, utilizing customized software should contribute to higher levels of productivity.</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-10-14 09:29:58', 1, '2022-11-02 09:07:48', 1),
(18, 'Website design services', 'website-design-services', '<p>Web design has the power to help you increase sales and improve your company’s revenue. Not only does your site’s design make the first impression, but it has the power to determine if someone becomes a sale for your business.</p>', '2022-10-21 07:28:08', 1, NULL, NULL),
(19, 'Business Website', 'business-website', '<p>Making a small business website is essential if you want to inform clients, explain your value proposition, build brand awareness, and boost sales.</p>', '2022-11-04 09:43:49', 1, NULL, NULL),
(20, 'Billing Software Management', 'billing-software-management', '<p>The billing software assists in collecting online payments for invoices, tracking payments, and managing customer data as it pertains to billing and invoicing.&nbsp;</p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-09 08:56:22', 1, NULL, NULL),
(21, 'Food Delivery Application', 'food-delivery-application', '<p>The introduction of technology has caused businesses to undergo rapid change. On top of that, since the market for on-demand meal delivery is booming, food ordering and delivery businesses do require mobile apps.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-11 09:23:05', 1, NULL, NULL),
(22, 'Inventory Management System', 'inventory-anagement-system', '<p>Many businesses have shifted from exclusively utilising inventory management systems only to keep track of inventory and report on it to using them to plan, project, and fill customer orders and increase profitability.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-18 09:44:15', 1, NULL, NULL),
(23, 'Inventory Management System', 'inventory-management-system', '<p>Many businesses have shifted from exclusively utilizing inventory management systems only to keep track of inventory and report on it to using them to plan, project, and fill customer orders and increase profitability.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-18 09:45:55', 1, NULL, NULL),
