(2, 'GRAPHIC DESIGNER', '<h3><strong>Job Summary</strong></h3><p>We\'re looking for a highly creative graphic designer who can translate conceptual ideas into visual representations. By collaborating with multiple departments within the company, the graphic designer should be able to take direction from written or spoken ideas and transform them into a meaningful design. If you think you have what it takes to bring ideas to life with visual impact, we want to hear from you. A portfolio showcasing creative work related to graphic design is necessary ( share on <a href=\"mailto:hr@codepilot.in\"><strong>hr@codepilot.in</strong></a> )</p><p>Open Position: 1 | Experience: 0-3 years</p><h3><strong>Responsibilities and Duties:</strong></h3><ul><li>Should have expertise in softwares like Adobe After Effects, Illustrator, Premiere Pro, Photoshop</li><li>Examine design briefs to determine requirements.</li><li>Create visuals based on the specifications.;</li><li>For each graphic, use the appropriate colours and layouts.;</li><li>Should be skilled at creating animated videos.</li><li>Collaborate with copywriters and managers to create the final design.;</li><li>After receiving feedback, revise your designs.;</li></ul><h3><strong>Work Days: Monday to Saturday</strong></h3><p>If interested please send your resume at <a href=\"mailto:hr@codepilot.in\"><strong>hr@codepilot.in</strong></a></p>', 'graphic', '2022-09-09 07:27:25', 0, '2022-09-09 08:58:16', 1);

